Home Town Real Estate Of Canon City

data.description: Come check out this charming home in the heart of beautiful Canon City. This home features fresh paint and new vinyl flooring, as well as hardwood in the bedroom and living room. With a fully privacy fenced in back yard, you can give Fido the home of their dreams too! Centrally located: grocery stores, shopping, restaurants, the post office, schools and many many other amenities are only blocks away! This would make a wonderful starter home or rental income property. Access to Highway 50 is easy, making this a great location if you're commuting to Pueblo or Colorado Springs. If a conveniently located, charming home is on your bucket list; let this home check the box!
